FBIS3-31982 "drlat020_o_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 Colombia Army Appoints New Tarqui Battalion Commander PA2801162094 Santa Fe de Bogota EL TIEMPO in Spanish 26 Jan 94 p 6c PA2801162094 Santa Fe de Bogota EL TIEMPO Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Tunja -- The Army has appointed Lieutenant Colonel Gilberto Morales Garcia as the new commander of the Tarqui Battalion at Sogamoso. Morales replaces Lt. Col. Ramiro Guevara Morera, who died when his helicopter crashed in the Sogamoso area two weeks ago. Morales will assume command next Friday.
